rn Qiraji idols would work quite well, as their quality is superior.Bring me the ring and idols and I'll create a powerful ring for you,  druid.8701The rings worn by the Qiraji lieutenants are rumored to grant them formidable abilities.  The corrupted gems that adorn them could, in theory, be swapped out with more pure materials to create uncorrupted versions of the rings.The gems that adorn Qiraji idols would work quite well, as their quality is superior.Bring me the ring and idols and I'll create a powerful ring for you, .8702The rings worn by the Qiraji lieutenants are rumored to grant them formidable abilities.  The corrupted gems that adorn them could, in theory, be swapped out with more pure materials to create uncorrupted versions of the rings.The gems that adorn Qiraji idols would work quite well, as their quality is superior.Bring me the ring and idols and I'll create a powerful ring for you, .8703The rings worn by the Qiraji lieutenants are rumored to grant them formidable abilities.  The corrupted gems that adorn them could, in theory, be swapped out with more pure materials to create uncorrupted versions of the rings.The gems that adorn Qiraji idols would work quite well, as their quality is superior.Bring me the ring and idols and I'll create a powerful ring for you, .8704The rings worn by the Qiraji lieutenants are rumored to grant them formidable abilities.  The corrupted gems that adorn them could, in theory, be swapped out with more pure materials to create uncorrupted versions of the rings.The gems that adorn Qiraji idols would work quite well, as their quality is superior.Bring me the ring and idols and I'll create a powerful ring for you, .8705The Qiraji and their servants wield items made with the rarest and finest materials: bones from gargantuan ancient creatures, gems from the depths of the earth, metals pure and strong.Just the sight of Qiraji artifacts fills me with an urge to practice my craft with their shattered and smelted pieces.  Prove your allegiance to the Circle, , and I will make you a powerful weapon from the finest Qiraji materials.8706The Qiraji and their servants wield items made with the rarest and finest materials: bones from gargantuan ancient creatures, gems from the depths of the earth, metals pure and strong.Just the sight of Qiraji artifacts fills me with an urge to practice my craft with their shattered and smelted pieces.  Prove your allegiance to the Circle, , and I will make you a powerful weapon from the finest Qiraji materials.8707The Qiraji and their servants wield items made with the rarest and finest materials: bones from gargantuan ancient creatures, gems from the depths of the earth, metals pure and strong.Just the sight of Qiraji artifacts fills me with an urge to practice my craft with their shattered and smelted pieces.  Prove your allegiance to the Circle, , and I will make you a powerful weapon from the finest Qiraji materials.8708The Qiraji and their servants wield items made with the rarest and finest materials: bones from gargantuan ancient creatures, gems from the depths of the earth, metals pure and strong.Just the sight of Qiraji artifacts fills me with an urge to practice my craft with their shattered and smelted pieces.  Prove your allegiance to the Circle, , and I will make you a powerful weapon from the finest Qiraji materials.8709The Qiraji and their servants wield items made with the rarest and finest materials: bones from gargantuan ancient creatures, gems from the depths of the earth, metals pure and strong.Just the sight of Qiraji artifacts fills me with an urge to practice my craft with their shattered and smelted pieces.  Prove your allegiance to the Circle, , and I will make you a powerful weapon from the finest Qiraji materials.8710The Qiraji and their servants wield items made with the rarest and finest materials: bones from gargantuan ancient creatures, gems from the depths of the earth, metals pure and s